Articles.Content:
Wow, I didn't expected that this would "impact" like this! Thanks for all your positive feedback! 

@Leszek: I haven't really thought about the colors yet, haha ![:D](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif)

@sp1989: I want to make them more detailed as Stock parts, but not too detailed as Launchers Pack, so the part detail level will be somewhere in the middle of those two. ![:)](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif)

So yes, I will make it stockalike, at least a bit, for example those characteristic black/white stripes on the engine mounts, and as for the tanks, I thought a combination of white and grey could look good. The models you can see above will probably get a remake or at least an overhaul, to make them visually mire interesting. ![:)](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif)
